{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/1-_title_-_ALL.gif?t=1737036038\" /><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Formula 2D - Steer To Persevere</strong> is a top of the line Formula Racing game where mild similarities with F1 are entirely coincidental</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Create and customize your team \ud83c\udfce\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Upgrade your facilities to improve your car \ud83c\udfd7\ufe0f </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Become the world champion in campaign mode \ud83c\udfc1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Compete with players worldwide in asynchronous multiplayer \ud83c\udfc6</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/Stacks.png?t=1737036038\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Compete against player all over the world in asynchronous Races. </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/2-_Online_play_-_ALL.gif?t=1737036038\" />Challenge drivers from every corner of the globe in thrilling races. Submit your best lap times and see how you stack up against other racers. With every race, you'll face new opponents and ever-changing conditions. Can you consistently outpace the competition and secure your place at the top of the global leaderboards ?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/Stacks_grey.png?t=1737036038\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play Co-op with up to 8 players </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/Splitscreen_Gif_Txt.gif?t=1737036038\" />Splitscreen, shared screen or even Steam Remote play. Have friends join your race at any time on any mode with drop in Co-op. So join forces and aim for the constructor's championship in career mode or compete with players world wide in asynchronous races ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/Stacks_green.png?t=1737036038\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Participate in weekly challenges that emulate the real world championships</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/6-_Weekly_challenge_-_ALL.gif?t=1737036038\" />Test your skills in dynamic weekly challenges inspired by real-world racing events. Each week brings new tracks, different weather conditions, and unique racing scenarios. Compete for glory, exclusive rewards, and the chance to prove that you have what it takes to be a true champion in both virtual and real racing worlds.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/Stacks_grey.png?t=1737036038\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Overtake on track or strategize your way to victory</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/5-_overtake_-_ALL.gif?t=1737036038\" /><br>DRS, pit stops, weather changes\u2014use every tool at your disposal to outsmart and outpace your rivals. Every decision counts.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/Stacks.png?t=1737036038\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Create your own team and upgrade your facilities </strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/3-_factory_-_ALL.gif?t=1737036038\" />Build and manage your own racing team from the ground up. Develop your headquarters, attract top-tier sponsors, and invest in cutting-edge technology. Upgrade your car's performance, improve your team's efficiency, and turn your fledgling team into a powerhouse. Guide your team through the seasons and aim to become the world champion.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/Stacks_green.png?t=1737036038\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Design the car you want</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/4-_design_-_ALL.gif?t=1737036038\" />Unleash your creativity and  design your perfect race car. Customize every detail of the livery to ensure your vehicle stands out on the track. With endless customization options, you can create a car that not only looks amazing but also delivers peak performance in every race.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/Stacks_grey.png?t=1737036038\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Climb the ranks online and unlock a ton of rewards</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/7-_unloackable_-_ALL.gif?t=1737036038\" />Rise through the online leaderboards by competing in intense, skill-based races. Prove your mettle against other players and earn a variety of exciting rewards. Unlock new cars, customizations, and exclusive content as you progress. Can you reach the top and claim the ultimate rewards?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2828140/extras/Stacks.png?t=1737036038\" />Enjoy all the great features that make the biggest motorsport ever<br>- 20+ Tracks from all over the world<br>- Weather changes<br>- Tyre strategies<br>- DRS management<br>- And so much more